title: Python Convert String Date into datetime Object format
description:
Python Convert String Date into datetime Object format
#strptime === String to datetime object = strptime
#strftime === datetime object to other formats

import datetime

string_date = "2019-01-13 18:40:51"

format = "%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S"

datetime_object = datetime.datetime.strptime(string_date, format)

print "Datetime: ", datetime_object
print "Hour: ", datetime_object.hour
print "Minute: ", datetime_object.minute
print "Second: ", datetime_object.second
